item.title: Nebraska Baseball 2020-2021
item.description: How does the Nebraska Baseball team of 2021 compare to other power 5 schools? With COVID limiting their season to only Big Ten play, the Huskers found their way to a Fayetteville regional as Big Ten champions. They then faced a fierce Arkansas team in the regional championship where they faced defeat. library(tidyverse)

item.title: About Braden Robinson
item.description: I am currently a senior at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I am double majoring in sports media and communications, as well as graphic design. I’m interested in the sports media field as well as sports graphics on social media.
